OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fvariable, often large, amounts of
OL,7,Fcloud but also clear spells.
OL,8,FTemperatures will fall slightly lower
OL,9,Fcompared to Friday night. Winds light
OL,10,Fand variable.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FMainly dry with often large
OL,13,Famounts of cloud, but some bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Light onshore winds will
OL,15,Fkeep coastal areas cooler, also bring
OL,16,Fthe chance of patchy low cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
