OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FPredominantly dry and becoming very
OL,7,Fwarm or hot, with the heat peaking
OL,8,FTuesday. Chance of occasional mist or
OL,9,Flow cloud along the coast. Humid and
OL,10,Fvery warm nights.
